    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7488733/" class="title-link">什么是复合多数民主，及民主的效率问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7488733"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3126457/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3126457-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3126457/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">三石</span>
